A simple program that demonstrates how to program a magnetometer
on the Raspberry Pi and includes tilt compensation.

Both the BerryIMUv1 and BerryIMUv2 are supported.


To compile;
gcc -g -o compass_tutorial04 compass_tutorial04.c -lSDL `sdl-config --cflags` `sdl-config --libs` -lm -lSDL_ttf -lSDL_image -lSDL_gfx -lSDL


To run;
sudo ./compass_tutorial04

More info here;
http://ozzmaker.com/compass04/

